title: Euryproctus
text:
Euryproctus is a genus of <a href="wasps">wasps</a> belonging to the family <a href="Ichneumonidae">Ichneumonidae</a>.
The genus was <a href="species%20description">first described</a> by Holmgren in 1855.
The genus has <a href="cosmopolitan%20distribution">cosmopolitan distribution</a>.
